obj_root_law_sections_2_content:
  string
  line 2
  line `recorded in writing, and shall be subject to appeal to the Revenue Authorities to whom they are`
  line subordinate.
  line ______
  line `FORM A.`
  line `Whereas you are the Owner (Occupa nt as the case may be) of the field`
  line `In the Village of you are hereby required to fix boundary`
  line `marks to the said field (by ridging or raising mounds of earth at the angles, or in such other mode as may`
  line `be determined) or to r epair its present boundary, within days from this date, in default of which the`
  line `same will be done by the Government Officers, and the cost recovered from you under Act III. of 1846.`
obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes:
  string
